name: collage: 3099CE
description:
The genesis of my collage series. I pulled inspiration and imagery from my favorite sci-fi feat. Blade Runner, 5th Element, Dredd, and Cowboy Bebop.
As a set designer, my favorite part of any sci-fi is the futuristic street market- an overload of textures, colors, characters, alien wares, mixed languages over tattered banners need neon signs.
